data.description: Welcome to 21532 Ives, a gem nestled in the heart of California City! This delightful home offers a generous layout comprising 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an additional bonus room. A versatile space perfect for a home office, guest room, or hobby area.Features include, tile flooring, gorgeous granite countertops, a large master suite with private bathroom and walk in closet, an indoor laundry room, and more! Got toys? No problem! This home sits on a GIGANTIC LOT of over 15,000 sq ft and features an extra long driveway! Perfect for any vehicles or even an RV! So don't wait. Call today and make this Dream Home your reality!
